Here it is. Uber 1337 and undetectable. You can either make it type humanily or just send the text straight to the client (suggested only if you want to spam).

Download It

Copy 'n Paste it:

[code]{=========================================================}
//-Dizzy-AutoTalk-
//Version:1.0
//Made By: Dizzy
//Release Date: 5/8/06
//Setup At Line(s) 13-18
//Start At: Bank, Populated Area, Etc. (Good for selling stuff).
//You may, use this script with no cost.
//You may not, steal this coding and say that you made it/re-produce
//script.
program DAT; //Please Do Not Change This

//All Code is below this\
const{–>SETUP<---------------------------------------}
TalkF2 = ‘TEXTGOESHERE’;//Press F2 For It To Auto Type
TalkF3 = ‘TEXTGOESHERE’;//Press F3 For It To Auto Type
TalkF4 = ‘TEXTGOESHERE’;//Press F4 For It To Auto Type
TalkF5 = ‘TEXTGOESHERE’;//Press F5 For It To Auto Type
TalkF6 = ‘TEXTGOESHERE’;//Press F6 For It To Auto Type
TypeHuman = ‘Yes’;//Put Yes For Human Mode And No For Spam
//Human Mode==>Types Like A Human<==\
//Spam Mode==>Does Not Type Like Human<==\
{–>END OF SETUP<-------------------------------------}
Var a:integer; //Please Do not Edit Lines 19-103
{.include Squig.txt}
Procedure DAT;
Begin
a:=0;
Repeat
a:= (a+1)
Wait(275);
If (IsFKeyDown(2))Then
Begin
a:=(a+1)
If(TypeHuman=‘Yes’)Then
Begin
SendKeysHuman(TalkF2 + chr(13))
end;
If(TypeHuman=‘No’)Then
Begin
Sendkeys(TalkF2 + chr(13))
end;
end;
If (IsFKeyDown(3))Then
Begin
a:=(a+1)
If(TypeHuman=‘Yes’)Then
Begin
SendKeysHuman(TalkF3 + chr(13))
end;
If(TypeHuman=‘No’)Then
Begin
SendKeys(TalkF3 + chr(13))
end;
end;
If (IsFKeyDown(4))Then
Begin
a:=(a+1)
If(TypeHuman=‘Yes’)Then
Begin
SendKeysHuman(TalkF4 + chr(13))
End;
If(TypeHuman=‘No’)Then
Begin
SendKeys(TalkF4 + chr(13))
end;
end;
If (IsFKeyDown(5))Then
Begin
a:=(a+1)
If(TypeHuman=‘Yes’)Then
Begin
SendKeysHuman(TalkF5 + chr(13))
End;
If(TypeHuman=‘No’)Then
Begin
SendKeys(TalkF5 + chr(13))
end;
End;
If (IsFKeyDown(6))Then
Begin
a:=(a+1)
If(TypeHuman=‘Yes’)Then
Begin
SendKeysHuman(TalkF6 + chr(13))
End;
If(TypeHuman=‘No’)Then
Begin
SendKeys(TalkF6 + chr(13))
end;
End;
Until(a<=0)
end;

Begin
DAT;
end.
